=head1 NAME

S319OSSO - Collects Oracle OpenSSO Information

=head1 DESCRIPTION

This module collects information related to Oracle OpenSSO, formerly known as
Sun OpenSSO Enterprise.

The following reports can be generated and are regrouped under
C<Oracle OpenSSO>:

=head1 REPORTS

=cut

echo tput('bold'),'Processing OSSO module ...',tput('off')

# Initialization
var $INS_HOME = getSetting('OSSO_INSTANCE_HOME','')

var $TOC = '%TOC%'
var $TOP = '[[#Top][Back to top]]'
pretoc '1:Oracle OpenSSO'

# Load the common macros
run library()

=head2 Instance Files

Gathers OpenSSO instance-related configuration and log files.

=cut

if testDir('d',$INS_HOME)
{debug ' Inside OSSO module, collecting the instance files'
 pretoc '2:Instance Files'
 call sort_files(3,0,catFile($INS_HOME,'bootstrap'),\
                     catFile($INS_HOME,'install.log'),\
                     grepDir(catDir($INS_HOME,'opensso','debug'),'^\.+$','pv'),\
                     grepDir(catDir($INS_HOME,'opensso','log'),'^\.+$','pv'),\
                     grepDir(catDir($INS_HOME,'opensso','stat'),'^\.+$','pv'))
 unpretoc
}

unpretoc

